wiki.summary: "Padam Padam" is the Grammy Award winning song by Australian singer Kylie Minogue, released on 18 May 2023 as the lead single from her sixteenth studio album, "Tension". It was written by Ina Wroldsen and Peter Rycroft, and produced by Lostboy. The music video was directed by Sophie Muller and released the same day as the song. Read more on Last.fm.
